body:
### expected behaviour
when i share a folder with public link, and open that link in chrome (which had no session of owncloud open before) i expect to see the shared folder.

### actual behaviour
the page does not finish loading.

### steps to reproduce
1. share a folder (the example photo folder containing 3 pictures) with link
2. copy the link
3. paste it into chrome, press enter
4. chrome will not finish loading.

the same link pasted into the firefox (used to create the link) properly shows the shared folder, both when logged in, as well as after logging out. it also works in internet explorer, so it seems to be chrome-specific.

### server configuration
operating system: ubuntu server 12.04.3 lts
web server: apache 2.4.6
database: mysql ver 14.14 distrib 5.5.34
php version: 5.5.5-1
owncloud version: 6.0.0b5

### client configuration
browser: firefox 25.0.1 / chrome 27.0.1453.110 / internet explorer 10.0.9200.16736
operating system: windows 7

